WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.010 --> 00:00:05.420
Welcome to Budi Sun Resort

00:00:05.420 --> 00:00:10.149
we are a familial diving resort in
Indonesia on the island of Flores

00:00:10.149 --> 00:00:13.619
next to the city of Maumere.

00:00:13.619 --> 00:00:17.720
Maumere Bay has a lot to offer to divers:

00:00:17.720 --> 00:00:22.159
you can find a lot of different fish,
coral and types of slopes.

00:00:22.159 --> 00:00:24.430
In Budi Sun Resort, the next

00:00:24.430 --> 00:00:27.189
diving spot is right at your door:

00:00:27.189 --> 00:00:31.179
our house reef offers a big part of the marine
diversity

00:00:31.179 --> 00:00:34.090
of the Flores Sea.

00:00:34.090 --> 00:00:36.010
Our diving guides

00:00:36.010 --> 00:00:40.850
are experienced and know the best
dive spots in Maumere Bay.

00:00:40.850 --> 00:00:45.200
Your security is important for us:

00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:50.590
Our employees are certified following
international security standards

00:00:50.590 --> 00:00:56.390
and we use only high quality equipment like
Mares, AquaLung and

00:00:56.390 --> 00:00:58.100
Sherwood.

00:00:58.100 --> 00:01:02.649
Our DAN rescue equipment is on board
on all our diving trips and

00:01:02.649 --> 00:01:04.089
the emergency plan is prepared to bring
you

00:01:04.089 --> 00:01:10.670
to the next decompression chamber on Bali
in case of an emergency.

00:01:10.670 --> 00:01:12.330
In addition to our diving trips,

00:01:12.330 --> 00:01:15.220
we offer you tours to discover Flores.

00:01:15.220 --> 00:01:19.130
There are numerous options, starting from climbing
the active volcano Egon

00:01:19.130 --> 00:01:22.870
and not ending with visiting the
hot springs in the jungle.

00:01:22.870 --> 00:01:26.540
Budi Sun offers 4 different room categories:

00:01:26.540 --> 00:01:27.970
 

00:01:27.970 --> 00:01:30.890
Sea View Bungalow has its own terrace

00:01:30.890 --> 00:01:33.350
with view on the sea and the garden;

00:01:33.350 --> 00:01:38.180
Garden Double Bungalow offers a traditional roof construction and

00:01:38.180 --> 00:01:40.000
partial sea view;

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:42.460
In the main building you will find the
Sea View Room

00:01:42.460 --> 00:01:47.380
overlooking the fish pond and the sea and
our Garden Rooms - with a garden

00:01:47.380 --> 00:01:49.930
view.

00:01:49.930 --> 00:01:54.430
All of our bungalows and rooms have
air conditioning and a bathroom with

00:01:54.430 --> 00:01:56.830
hot and cold water.

00:01:56.830 --> 00:02:01.610
You can relax on bamboo sun loungers or hammocks at the beach

00:02:01.610 --> 00:02:06.650
or at our sweet water pool that is sun-protected 

00:02:06.650 --> 00:02:10.019
by a traditional roof construction.

00:02:10.019 --> 00:02:14.219
Our architecture is influenced by the  

00:02:14.219 --> 00:02:15.849
different cultures on Flores.

00:02:15.849 --> 00:02:20.229
The roofs of the bungalows, the different
patterns of the bamboo mats

00:02:20.229 --> 00:02:24.339
and the furniture are from different regions of
the island,

00:02:24.339 --> 00:02:26.299
lamps and decorations

00:02:26.299 --> 00:02:30.299
show the craftsmanship and culture of Flores.

00:02:31.129 --> 00:02:33.969
You will find a lot of different indonesian fruit

00:02:33.969 --> 00:02:39.249
flowers and plants in our garden.
These are also very often

00:02:39.249 --> 00:02:44.949
used as a medicine by the native people of Flores.

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:47.040
Our restaurant serves fresh fruit from our garden

00:02:47.140 --> 00:02:50.180
and the market in Maumere

00:02:50.180 --> 00:02:51.909
for breakfast.

00:02:51.909 --> 00:02:55.359
In the evening, our restaurant uses fresh ingredients

00:02:55.359 --> 00:02:59.369
to prepare local and international food for you

00:02:59.369 --> 00:03:03.079
and you can close the day while enjoying the

00:03:03.079 --> 00:03:05.339
the beautiful sunset at the beach.

00:03:05.339 --> 00:03:10.019
Come and visit us and meet Joseph and Erman

00:03:10.019 --> 00:03:12.609
who will welcome you at the reception of our resort.

